Class Administrator

  • java.lang.Object
    • api.User
      • api.Administrator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Administrator
extends api.User
implements java.io.Serializable
    Administrator is a type of user. Administrator has access to modify products and categories in the system. Administartor inherits User class. An administrator's information includes:
    • UserID
    • password
    • Background information
    Version:
    1.0
